      <title>欧盟对特朗普的全球关税罢工的重视“强大计划”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/eu-readies-strong-plan-against-trump-s-global-tariff-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）遵循他的威胁，将利用广泛的选择来对美国进行报复，并在本周本周在集团上征收所谓的互惠关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/eu-readies-strong-plan-against-trump-s-global-tariff-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 07:39:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
